settings.description: Test some of your skills with the Tanooki Suit in this brief adventure up in the sky!
Careful, these creepy crawling beetles just love roaming around on all these wooden walkways! think you can find their hidden Tanooki suit though?
Venture through a switch-and-money-filled world of speedrunning, careful timing, precise jumps, and more! There's also an E-Coin up high in space, waiting to be found!
BOO!! rawr very spoopy :3      and very janky
Luigi has teamed up with bowser to take over the mushroom kingdom using the advanced P-wing, Mario must take the advanced P-wing from the chest to halfway stop the invasion.
